headline: Prudential and LPL Collaborate to Expand Access to Retirement Security
summary: NEWARK, N.J. & SAN DIEGO, September 22, 2025--Prudential Financial, Inc. and LPL Financial LLC today announced a further expansion of their relationship, as the two firms collaborate to bring to market an Insurance Overlay retirement lifetime income strategy for LPL’s managed accounts platform.
